GET http://192.168.3.127/status


### Get the current status of the light
GET http://192.168.3.127/light/0

### Toggle the light on or off
GET http://192.168.3.127/light/0?turn=toggle

### Start dimming the light up to maximum brightness (using the configured fade rate)
GET http://192.168.3.127/light/0?dim=up&step=100

### Start dimming the light down to minimum brightness (using the configured fade rate)
GET http://192.168.3.127/light/0?dim=down&step=100

### Stop dimming the light (hold the current brightness)
GET http://192.168.3.127/light/0?dim=stop
